{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/align-an-item-horizontally-using-justify-self","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-grid","demoType":null,"title":"Poravnajte komadi ravnomjerno korišćenjem justify-self","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U CSS Grid, sadržaj svake ćelije nalazi se unutar kutije nazvane <dfn>seli</dfn>. Možete poravnati prostor sadržaja unutar svoje ćelije koristeći svojstvo <code>justify-self</code> na elementu mrežice. Podrazumevano, ovo svojstvo ima vrednost <code>stretch</code>, što će učiniti da sadržaj popuni celu širinu ćelije. Ovo svojstvo CSS Grid takođe prihvata druge vrednosti:</p>\n<p><code>start</code>: inapanga maudhui upande wa kushoto wa seli,</p>\n<p><code>center</code>: inapanga maudhui katikati ya seli,</p>\n<p><code>end</code>: inapanga maudhui upande wa kulia wa seli.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a90374338fddaf9a66b5d3a","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristi atribut <code>justify-self</code> da sastavi deo sa klasom <code>item2</code> na sredini.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pByETK/cJbpKHq","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301122,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/align-an-item-horizontally-using-justify-self"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item1 {\r\n    background: LightSkyBlue;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .item2 {\r\n    background: LightSalmon;\r\n    /* Only change code below this line */\r\n\r\n    \r\n    /* Only change code above this line */\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    background: PaleTurquoise;\r\n  }\r\n  .item4 {\r\n    background: LightPink;\r\n  }\r\n  .item5 {\r\n    background: PaleGreen;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .container {\r\n    font-size: 40px;\r\n    min-height: 300px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    background: LightGray;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-gap: 10px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n  <div class=\"item1\">1</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item2\">2</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item3\">3</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item4\">4</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item5\">5</div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Klasa <code>item2</code> treba da ima svojstvo <code>justify-self</code> sa vrednošću <code>center</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\r\n  code,\r\n  /.item2\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*justify-self\\s*?:\\s*?center\\s*?;[\\s\\S]*}/gi\r\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-grid","dashedName":"align-an-item-horizontally-using-justify-self","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-grid","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/align-an-item-vertically-using-align-self","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/use-grid-row-to-control-spacing","id":"5a90374338fddaf9a66b5d3a","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n  }\r\n</style>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/align-an-item-horizontally-using-justify-self"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}